                            This raffle is sponsored by <Link href="https://fenixsim.com/" target="_blank">Fenix Simulations</Link> and 
                            <Link href="https://inibuilds.com" target="_blank">iniBuilds</Link> with the following prizes available:
                        </p>
    
                        <ul class="mb-4">
                            <li>1x <Link href="https://fenixsim.com/a320/" target="_blank">Fenix A320</Link><span class="text-info">*</span></li>
                            <li>2x <Link href="https://inibuilds.com/pages/iniscenery" target="_blank">iniBuilds scenery</Link> of choice</li>
                        </ul>
    
                        <p class="mb-4">
                            To join the raffle, you need to acquire tickets.
                            You get a ticket for each completed flight that departs or arrives in a Norwegian aerodrome.
                            The more tickets you have, meaning the more airports you've flown to or from in Norway, the higher your winning chance is.
                        </p>
    
