                            <li>
                                You must fly online on VATSIM at 1x speed with a flight plan
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                The flight must depart or arrive at a Norwegian aerodrome
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                The flight must take place DAY XXth April between XX:00z and XX:00z
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                The flight can not have a Cross the Pond destination airport this day
                            </li>
